title: Frank Lloyd Wright March Balloons Stud Earring—Blue/Green
description:
Want style in spades? You're in the Wright place. These laser cut stainless steel and concrete earrings are inspired by a detail from a series of twelve unpublished covers for Liberty Magazine in 1927, created by Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867-1959). Rubber earring backs included. Made in the USA. Colors may vary in intensity. 

1 in.
